                <h1>Notre Dame men&#039;s basketball 2016-17 season preview </h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/28ce92c0-3cf5-4791-9816-25686ecf8409.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Senior&#x20;Steve&#x20;Vasturia&#x20;averaged&#x20;11.4&#x20;points&#x20;per&#x20;game&#x20;a&#x20;year&#x20;ago&#x20;and&#x20;will&#x20;be&#x20;another&#x20;crucial&#x20;piece&#x20;for&#x20;the&#x20;Fighting&#x20;Irish&#x20;this&#x20;season.&amp;nbsp&#x3B;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Senior Steve Vasturia averaged 11.4 points per game a year ago and will be another crucial piece for the Fighting Irish this season.&nbsp;</p>

                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
