                        <p><strong>One thing that needs to go right: </strong>Former role players Farrell and Steve Vasturia&nbsp;step into their expanded roles and&nbsp;replace the lost production of Jackson and Auguste on both ends of the floor.&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>One thing that could go wrong: </strong>Notre Dame's subpar defense forces them to win high-scoring games all season and the Fighting Irish fail to&nbsp;muster enough points to string together long winning streaks.&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><strong></strong></p>
